    <item>
      <title>尽管价格居高不下，但非洲经济前景光明</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/africa-s-economic-outlook-brightens-even-as-price-remains-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，非洲的经济前景已经明朗，但面临着从美元复苏到致命干旱等风险，这些风险加剧了非洲已经遭受的“残酷鸡尾酒”冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/africa-s-economic-outlook-brightens-even-as-price-remains-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织考虑增加赞比亚资金以帮助应对干旱紧急情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/imf-considers-upping-zambia-funds-to-help-with-drought-emergency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织正在与赞比亚进行谈判，以增加对该国的融资，该国正遭受有记录以来最严重的干旱影响，而该国正刚刚摆脱极其缓慢的债务重组进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/imf-considers-upping-zambia-funds-to-help-with-drought-emergency</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约梅隆银行财富首席信息官表示，逢低买入比现金更好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/buying-this-dip-is-better-than-cash-bny-mellon-wealth-cio-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约梅隆银行财富管理部门首席投资官西尼德·科尔顿·格兰特 (Sinead Colton Grant) 表示，美国股市从上个月末创下的历史高位回落，为持有现金的投资者提供了买入机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/buying-this-dip-is-better-than-cash-bny-mellon-wealth-cio-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管面临压力，欧洲央行仍坚持对银行股息采取强硬立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ecb-sticks-with-tough-line-on-bank-dividends-despite-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强硬派和新任监事会主席克劳迪娅·布赫(Claudia Buch)的反对，高级监管机构试图软化欧洲央行对贷方股息和股票回购的立场，但这一努力却步履蹒跚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ecb-sticks-with-tough-line-on-bank-dividends-despite-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
